## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not reflect the most current developments in the school bus driver shortage. Additionally, the analysis relies on secondary sources, which may introduce biases or incomplete perspectives. Further research, including primary data collection and interviews with stakeholders, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.